As you aren't launching your application on a live server, you can use test payment gateway which seems to real usage gateway.

SSLcommerz - is your dummy API which gives all the functionality you need to get for a real-time system. The provided sandbox is need to test whether 
             your system is ready for succesful publication.
             
             
Official website : https://developer.sslcommerz.com/
Documentation : https://developer.sslcommerz.com/doc/v4/

Firstly, you have to create a sandbox account and use valid email where you will get credentials and login sslcommerz as merchant.
Login url : Merchant Panel URL: https://sandbox.sslcommerz.com/manage/              #You've to submit username and password which is registered by you.

Laravel integration repository : https://github.com/sslcommerz/SSLCommerz-Laravel
